column1: Regular traffic reports will resume Friday August 28 at 4:00 p.m.

column3: Traffic Alert for E High St:
column4: E High St is shutdown between Rose St and Stone Ave as KU works on repairs/replacement of a downed electrical pole and wires as a result of an earlier collision.

column3: Traffic Alert for E High St:
column4: Expected duration until 3 p.m. to 4 p.m.  Traffic is being diverted to either side of Rose St.  Motorists should plan routes accordingly during this time.

column3: Traffic Alert for E High St:
column4: Update 3:13 p.m. - E High St is back open.
